name: "Let Us Do It"  with The "A"mbiance Team-Mashtini and Pastatini Bars
description:
Mashtini and Pastatini Bars for your next party, great for any age group...a sure hit! Book your party today at our introductory prices they will not last long! Sweet Sixteens, Anniversaries, Retirement Parties Bridal/Baby Showers, Birthday Parties! 

Mashtini Bar-We start with creamy potatoes in martini glasses and your guest can pile on the toppings. Sour cream, scallions, bacon, cheddar cheese,bbq chop beef and or chicken breast. You name the event your guest will love it! 

Pastatini Bar-We start with your choice of pasta( spaghetti, vermicelli, angel hair, fettuccine, penne or bow tie) in martini glasses and your guest can pile on the toppings chunky beef marinara, plain marinara, alfredo, grilled chicken, seasoned shrimp,mushrooms, and assorted cheese!
